  Clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3499826eac4165742ba31bf5e372d3d2, type: 3}
  Subtitles: "I know right! And she\u2019s been such a good friend to me too, especially
    with the whole \u2018sister breaking into my apartment\u2019 thing\u2026 It\u2019s
    not really her fault, she can\u2019t help it, her dad refused to get her diagnosed
    with lactation sensitivity as an infant, and she\u2019s my sister\u2026 So I
    feel like I can\u2019t really tell her no, since I never called Child Proteciton
    Service on her as a kid. It\u2019s fine if I just leave it be, right?"
